CustomField.description:
JSON ZPL printer config for this job. Populated by Apex/Flow from the Printer__c record before firing the event. The server uses this to prepend a ^PW/^LL/^MD setup block if the label does not already include those commands.
Format: {"dpi":203,"width_dots":812,"height_dots":1218,"darkness":15,"prefix":"^FX optional"}
Leave blank to let the server auto-detect via SGD query and cache the result.
